0Z","msg":"頑固 mayday"},{"pid":"b80685335566c6cd89c7f138659a60bc5b0146f6","tid":840340,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"說了再見"},{"pid":"7d168b0dee80dba4a0a4bb55f82eff3d4ab35918","tid":840340,"uid":186765,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"我有幾首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dh4eydYk6EA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ddh4eydYk6EA&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=76f063f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dh4eydYk6EA</a><br />\n<br />\nmy little airport - 年輕的茶餐廳老闆娘<br />\n<br />\n這些年裡面 你都知我很少到別的店 <br />\n但若你最終給我來電 你可知道這感覺會點 <br />\n像一支小蠟燭的光點 讓漆黑的房滿佈光線<br />\n像打開考試試卷發現 突然所有答案都看得見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1YI6IBY2PwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1YI6IBY2PwA&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1d4ffb31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1YI6IBY2PwA</a><br />\n<br />\nMy Little Airport - Leo, Are You Still Jumping Out Of Windows In Expensive Clothes ?<br />\n<br />\nI hope you can think what I can think. <br />\nBecause I&rsquo;m so crazy, because I&rsquo;m so crazy. <br />\nCos I know you know what I don&rsquo;t know. <br />\nI know you can think what I can&rsquo;t think. <br />\nBecause you are special, because you&rsquo;re so special.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8FOHbL4km6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8FOHbL4km6U&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=eb9a51c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8FOHbL4km6U</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借火-麥浚龍<br />\n<br />\n就算不說一句都很清楚　<br />\n雙方都經過太多 只要接近別無期望　<br />\n夜了看電視的光 只要我們不問為何　<br />\n然後直至忘記誰是我 一起靜靜的過　<br />\n不需要太認識我 不渴望　<br />\n你不要令我多幾多渴望 你只要為我點一點火　<br />\n然後讓我此刻至少可度過 我可以令你差不多有快樂　<br />\n我可以為你點一點火 <br />\n然後望你輪廓　不講甚麼悲壯　<br />\n不想甚麼沮喪 煙圈悄悄墜落煙灰至少將心事証明燃燒過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93af3052e58a2424990a0c9999f9eea0bac6b83","tid":840340,"uid":59679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62f2c3b7632d81709f3b30cdea9894bf630eb90c","tid":840340,"uid":208726,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"睇埋mv先會喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24369cf96128b02b6732352eee4c04c1cb5a4510","tid":840340,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:31:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03fc8bdeca76c120f34f785fb09d2a77fa63bba4","tid":840340,"uid":59679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24369cf96128b02b6732352eee4c04c1cb5a4510","tid":840340,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f93af3052e58a2424990a0c9999f9eea0bac6b83","tid":840340,"uid":59679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62f2c3b7632d81709f3b30cdea9894bf630eb90c","tid":840340,"uid":208726,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"睇埋mv先會喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:31:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da52f512f2db2cade4724e91e6f95ba934196923","tid":840340,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:3